dispel some dangerous myths.

243
00:16:49,760 --> 00:16:52,440
But in doing so,
they made a key mistake,

244
00:16:52,520 --> 00:16:54,880
as you will see
right at the end of this clip.

245
00:16:55,440 --> 00:16:59,200
The federal government said
that half of all surgery patients

246
00:16:59,280 --> 00:17:03,680
