275
00:18:43,640 --> 00:18:46,400
and oxy-branded
stuffed plush toys,

276
00:18:46,520 --> 00:18:49,240
and if you think we didn't get
hold of one of those,

277
00:18:49,320 --> 00:18:51,600
you have never watched
this show before.

278
00:18:51,720 --> 00:18:56,040
Because yes, here he is.
And yes, he is my new best friend,

279
00:18:56,240 --> 00:18:58,200
and yes, his name is Harold.

280
00:18:58,560 --> 00:19:02,320
Purdue, this is the perfect
choice of mascot.

281
00:19:02,520 --> 00:19:05,600
Much like a gorilla, OxyContin
might seem appealing,

282
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:09,400
but if you're not careful,
it will tear your fucking life apart.

283
00:19:09,920 --> 00:19:12,080
Won't you, Harold ?
Yes, he will.

284
00:19:13,640 --> 00:19:17,960
Purdue distributed inspirational videos
like "I Got My Life Back",

285
00:19:18,040 --> 00:19:22,520
seven patients whose lives were
turned around by OxyContin.

286
00:19:23,080 --> 00:19:27,080
Since I've been on this new medication,
I have not missed one day of work

287
00:19:27,160 --> 00:19:28,880
